'''独立广场'''（{{lang-id|'''Medan Merdeka'''}}）是印度尼西亚首都[[雅加达|雅加达]]市中心的一座大型广场<ref>Kuoni - Far East, A world of difference. Page 93. Published 1999 by Kuoni Travel & JPM Publications</ref>，面积达1平方公里，为[[按规模排列的广场列表|世界最大广场之一]]<ref>{{cite book |url= http://books.google.co.id/books?id=ktv0_me9x2UC&pg=PA85&lpg=PA85&dq=merdeka+square+jakarta+measured&source=bl&ots=i9l53Vq8qG&sig=z94pW1rYclbYD_d1SUF0GDQIhWg&hl=id&sa=X&ei=OoBqT4r5N8X5rAfruMSlAg&ved=0CFwQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=merdeka%20square%20jakarta%20measured&f=false |title= Indonesia Handbook, 3rd, page 85|author= Joshua Eliot, Liz Capaldi, Jane Bickersteth|year= 2001 |work= |publisher= Footprint Travel Guides|accessdate=21 March 2012}}</ref>。广场中心矗立着[[印尼国家纪念塔|印尼国家纪念塔]]<ref>[http://www.jakarta-hotel.asia/destination_guide#_741354976 Jakarta guide] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531033843/http://www.jakarta-hotel.asia/destination_guide |date=2010-05-31 }}</ref>，经常举办[[阅兵|阅兵]]、[[游行|游行]]、[[示威|示威]]活动。该广场为周末受雅加达人欢迎的运动休闲地点<ref name="Indonesia Travel">{{cite web|url=http://www.indonesia.travel/en/discover-indonesia/region-detail/30/dki-jakarta|title=Discover Indonesia: DKI Jakarta|author=|date=|work=|publisher=Indonesia travel|accessdate=15 July 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120530011617/http://indonesia.travel/en/discover-indonesia/region-detail/30/dki-jakarta|archivedate=2012年5月30日}}</ref>。它的周围是重要的政府建筑，如独立宫<ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=http://www.smarttravelasia.com/Jakarta.htm |title=A detailed travel guide to Jakarta |access-date=2013-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101222115825/http://smarttravelasia.com/Jakarta.htm |archive-date=2010-12-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[印尼国家博物馆|印尼国家博物馆]]、最高法院和政府各部。在[[荷屬東印度|荷屬東印度]]殖民地时期，该广场被称为“国王广场”（荷兰语：''Koningsplein''）<ref name="asiarooms1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.asiarooms.com/en/travel-guide/indonesia/jakarta/jakarta-popular-destinations/merdeka-square-in-jakarta.html |title=Merdeka Square in Jakarta |access-date=2013-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309110550/http://www.asiarooms.com/en/travel-guide/indonesia/jakarta/jakarta-popular-destinations/merdeka-square-in-jakarta.html |archive-date=2012-03-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

独立广场是雅加达乃至整个印尼的心脏，周围有许多重要的政府及文化机构<ref name=autogenerated1 />。美国大使馆亦位于广场以南<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.time.com/time/travel/article/0,31542,1944678,00.html |title=Sense of Place: Jakarta - TIME |access-date=2013-06-01 |archive-date=2013-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826210606/http://www.time.com/time/travel/article/0,31542,1944678,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

